CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Women and men, some wearing name tags, including Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence in center talking to woman wearing light colored short sleeved blouse and striped skirt, in the Office of the Mayor at the City County Building
